{"lineNumber":136379,"originalJapaneseLine":"部屋の中でハウゼルがスタスタと歩き、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel walked briskly inside the room,"},

{"lineNumber":136380,"originalJapaneseLine":"ゴソゴソと何か音を立てている。","translatedEnglishLine":"making some rustling noises."},

{"lineNumber":136381,"originalJapaneseLine":"どうやら軽く掃除をしているらしい。","translatedEnglishLine":"It seemed she was doing some light cleaning."},

{"lineNumber":136382,"originalJapaneseLine":"その間、ランスはずっと息を潜め続けた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Meanwhile, Rance kept holding his breath the entire time."},

{"lineNumber":136383,"originalJapaneseLine":"（う、う〜む……暇だなあ……","translatedEnglishLine":"(Ugh... I'm so bored..."},

{"lineNumber":136384,"originalJapaneseLine":"　外の様子も見えんからちっとも楽しくない）","translatedEnglishLine":"I can't see outside either, so it's not fun at all.)"},

{"lineNumber":136385,"originalJapaneseLine":"（む……？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Hmm...?)"},

{"lineNumber":136386,"originalJapaneseLine":"気づけば、ハウゼルはランスの潜んでいる","translatedEnglishLine":"Before he knew it, Hausel was standing in front of the desk where Rance was hiding."},

{"lineNumber":136387,"originalJapaneseLine":"机の前に立っていた。","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":136388,"originalJapaneseLine":"　　＜そっ……＞","translatedEnglishLine":"<Softly...>"},

{"lineNumber":136389,"originalJapaneseLine":"机の上に本―おそらく文庫本―を","translatedEnglishLine":"The sound of placing a book—probably a paperback—on the desk reached Rance's ears."},

{"lineNumber":136390,"originalJapaneseLine":"置く音がランスの耳に届く。","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":136391,"originalJapaneseLine":"「また……こんな本借りちゃった……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I borrowed another book like this again...\""},

{"lineNumber":136392,"originalJapaneseLine":"トクントクンとハウゼルの胸が高鳴り、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel’s heart thumped rapidly,"},

{"lineNumber":136393,"originalJapaneseLine":"こくんと唾を飲み込んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"and she swallowed hard."},

{"lineNumber":136394,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},

{"lineNumber":136395,"originalJapaneseLine":"（おっ、そろそろ本を読むか？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Oh, is she about to start reading the book?)"},

{"lineNumber":136396,"originalJapaneseLine":"（およ？　またどっか行っちまったぞ？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Huh? She went somewhere again?)"},

{"lineNumber":136397,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハウゼルは一度部屋の入り口まで戻り、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel went back to the entrance of the room,"},

{"lineNumber":136398,"originalJapaneseLine":"戸締まりを確認、窓も開いてないか","translatedEnglishLine":"checked the locks and looked around to make sure the windows were closed."},

{"lineNumber":136399,"originalJapaneseLine":"部屋中を確認した。","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":136400,"originalJapaneseLine":"（途中で誰か入って来ないようにか……","translatedEnglishLine":"(So she was making sure no one would come in halfway through..."},

{"lineNumber":136401,"originalJapaneseLine":"　まるでやることが思春期のガキだな）","translatedEnglishLine":"She’s acting like a pubescent kid.)"},

{"lineNumber":136402,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},

{"lineNumber":136403,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハウゼルが椅子に座り、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel sat down on the chair,"},

{"lineNumber":136404,"originalJapaneseLine":"テーブルの中にいたランスは後ろに避けた。","translatedEnglishLine":"and Rance, who was inside the table, moved back."},

{"lineNumber":136405,"originalJapaneseLine":"（おととと……遂に本を読むか？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Whoa... is she finally going to read the book?)"},

{"lineNumber":136406,"originalJapaneseLine":"（お、おーーーーっ！）","translatedEnglishLine":"(O-ohhhh!)"},

{"lineNumber":136407,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハウゼルの足が、かすかに左右に開き、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel’s legs slightly parted left and right,"},

{"lineNumber":136408,"originalJapaneseLine":"スカートの中の下着がランスの眼前で露わになった。","translatedEnglishLine":"and the underwear under her skirt was revealed right before Rance’s eyes."},

{"lineNumber":136409,"originalJapaneseLine":"（こ、これはすごい……","translatedEnglishLine":"(Th-this is amazing..."},

{"lineNumber":136410,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おほほほ、眼福眼福……）","translatedEnglishLine":"Oh hohoho, what a delight to the eyes...)"},

{"lineNumber":136411,"originalJapaneseLine":"（って、いかんいかん。","translatedEnglishLine":"(Wait, no no."},

{"lineNumber":136412,"originalJapaneseLine":"　静かにせねば）","translatedEnglishLine":"I have to stay quiet.)"},

{"lineNumber":136413,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスはより一層、息を潜めた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Rance held his breath even more carefully."},

{"lineNumber":136414,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふう……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Phew...\""},

{"lineNumber":136415,"originalJapaneseLine":"既に緊張感が全身を包んでいるハウゼルは、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel, already wrapped in tension all over,"},

{"lineNumber":136416,"originalJapaneseLine":"一度熱っぽい溜め息を吐きだしてから本を開いた。","translatedEnglishLine":"let out a feverish sigh once and then opened the book."},

{"lineNumber":136417,"originalJapaneseLine":"（……本、読んでるらしいな）","translatedEnglishLine":"(...Looks like she’s reading the book.)"},

{"lineNumber":136418,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハウゼルは本に集中しているのだろう。","translatedEnglishLine":"Hausel was probably focused on the book."},

{"lineNumber":136419,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスの目の前の綺麗な両足は動くこともなく、","translatedEnglishLine":"The beautiful legs right in front of Rance’s eyes didn’t move at all,"}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜しゃわぁぁぁ……＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: <Shuwaaa... (sound of water running)>

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （なんだ、風呂に入ってるのか……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Oh, she's taking a bath...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （……暇だな）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (...I'm bored.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （ああ、いやいや。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Ah, no no.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここはジッと我慢の子。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have to be patient here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 赤子泣いても蓋取るな。我慢我慢）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if the baby cries, don’t remove the lid. Patience, patience.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （……ふわぁ、ねむ）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (...Yawn, sleepy.)
"Phew..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （お、戻ってきた戻ってきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Oh, she’s back, she’s back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 危うく眠ってしまうところだった）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I almost fell asleep.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やっぱり、気配を感じるような」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I knew it, I feel like someone’s presence..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （ギクッ……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Gasp...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……いえ、きっと過敏になってるのね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...No, I must just be overly sensitive."
(Phew...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部屋の中でハウゼルがスタスタと歩き、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel walked briskly inside the room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゴソゴソと何か音を立てている。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: making some rustling noises.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうやら軽く掃除をしているらしい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seemed she was doing some light cleaning.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その間、ランスはずっと息を潜め続けた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, Rance kept holding his breath the entire time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （う、う〜む……暇だなあ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Ugh... I'm so bored...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 外の様子も見えんからちっとも楽しくない）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can't see outside either, so it's not fun at all.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気づけば、ハウゼルはランスの潜んでいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before he knew it, Hausel was standing in front of the desk where Rance was hiding.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 机の前に立っていた。

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: <Softly...>

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 机の上に本―おそらく文庫本―を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The sound of placing a book—probably a paperback—on the desk reached Rance's ears.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 置く音がランスの耳に届く。
「また……こんな本借りちゃった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I borrowed another book like this again..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: トクントクンとハウゼルの胸が高鳴り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel’s heart thumped rapidly,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こくんと唾を飲み込んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and she swallowed hard.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （おっ、そろそろ本を読むか？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Oh, is she about to start reading the book?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （およ？　またどっか行っちまったぞ？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Huh? She went somewhere again?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルは一度部屋の入り口まで戻り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel went back to the entrance of the room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戸締まりを確認、窓も開いてないか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: checked the locks and looked around to make sure the windows were closed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部屋中を確認した。
（途中で誰か入って来ないようにか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (So she was making sure no one would come in halfway through...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まるでやることが思春期のガキだな）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She’s acting like a pubescent kid.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルが椅子に座り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel sat down on the chair,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テーブルの中にいたランスは後ろに避けた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Rance, who was inside the table, moved back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （おととと……遂に本を読むか？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Whoa... is she finally going to read the book?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （お、おーーーーっ！）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (O-ohhhh!)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルの足が、かすかに左右に開き、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel’s legs slightly parted left and right,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スカートの中の下着がランスの眼前で露わになった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the underwear under her skirt was revealed right before Rance’s eyes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （こ、これはすごい……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Th-this is amazing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おほほほ、眼福眼福……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh hohoho, what a delight to the eyes...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （って、いかんいかん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Wait, no no.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 静かにせねば）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have to stay quiet.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスはより一層、息を潜めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance held his breath even more carefully.
"Phew..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 既に緊張感が全身を包んでいるハウゼルは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel, already wrapped in tension all over,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一度熱っぽい溜め息を吐きだしてから本を開いた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: let out a feverish sigh once and then opened the book.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （……本、読んでるらしいな）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (...Looks like she’s reading the book.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルは本に集中しているのだろう。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel was probably focused on the book.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの目の前の綺麗な両足は動くこともなく、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The beautiful legs right in front of Rance’s eyes didn’t move at all,

originalJapaneseLine.description: The original line in Japanese exactly as it was in the input

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 置く音がランスの耳に届く。
「また……こんな本借りちゃった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I borrowed another book like this again..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: トクントクンとハウゼルの胸が高鳴り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel’s heart thumped rapidly,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こくんと唾を飲み込んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and she swallowed hard.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （おっ、そろそろ本を読むか？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Oh, is she about to start reading the book?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （およ？　またどっか行っちまったぞ？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Huh? She went somewhere again?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルは一度部屋の入り口まで戻り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel went back to the entrance of the room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戸締まりを確認、窓も開いてないか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: checked the locks and looked around to make sure the windows were closed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部屋中を確認した。
（途中で誰か入って来ないようにか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (So she was making sure no one would come in halfway through...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まるでやることが思春期のガキだな）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She’s acting like a pubescent kid.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルが椅子に座り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel sat down on the chair,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テーブルの中にいたランスは後ろに避けた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Rance, who was inside the table, moved back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （おととと……遂に本を読むか？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Whoa... is she finally going to read the book?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （お、おーーーーっ！）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (O-ohhhh!)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルの足が、かすかに左右に開き、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel’s legs slightly parted left and right,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スカートの中の下着がランスの眼前で露わになった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the underwear under her skirt was revealed right before Rance’s eyes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （こ、これはすごい……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Th-this is amazing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おほほほ、眼福眼福……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh hohoho, what a delight to the eyes...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （って、いかんいかん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Wait, no no.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 静かにせねば）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have to stay quiet.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスはより一層、息を潜めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance held his breath even more carefully.
"Phew..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 既に緊張感が全身を包んでいるハウゼルは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel, already wrapped in tension all over,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一度熱っぽい溜め息を吐きだしてから本を開いた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: let out a feverish sigh once and then opened the book.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （……本、読んでるらしいな）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (...Looks like she’s reading the book.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハウゼルは本に集中しているのだろう。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hausel was probably focused on the book.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの目の前の綺麗な両足は動くこともなく、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The beautiful legs right in front of Rance’s eyes didn’t move at all,
